Enum Class CardName

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<CardName>
com.model.card.CardName
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<CardName>, Constable
public enum CardName extends Enum<CardName>
The enum Card Name. Names of the different selectable cards in the game : ANGRY_MOB, THE_INQUISITION, POINTED_HAT, HOOKED_NOSE, BROOMSTICK, WART, DUCKING_STOOL, CAULDRON, EVIL_EYE, TOAD, BLACK_CAT, PET_NEWT.
